                "url": "/topics/objects"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/simon_greenleaf_320851",
        "quote": "In requiring this candor and simplicity of mind in those who would investigate the truth of our religion, Christianity demands nothing more than is readily conceded to every branch of human science.",
